g.text: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX ont: <http://coto.pj.aist.go.jp/ontologies/structured-manual#> PREFIX act: <http://coto.pj.aist.go.jp/ontologies/structured-manual/Action/> SELECT distinct ?label2 ?risk WHERE {{select * where {?action ont:Achieve+ act:1.?action rdfs:label?label.filter regex(?label, "")}}{select * where {?action2 ont:Achieve+ ?action.?action2 rdfs:label?label2.filter(LANG(?label2)='ja')}}{select * where {?action2 ont:hasRisk?risk.}}}
